{"tid":2412493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人知 係一千年前既今日，中國正逢人類歷史上最強既皇朝，經歷緊史上最輝煌既盛世","createTime":"2021-02-18T05:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T10:29:29.000Z","uid":52658,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"83b3dd6d6500fe998cb9432597dd5c721104bef7","tid":2412493,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:17:21.000Z","msg":"公元1021既既中國<br />\n係北宋宋仁宗時期<br />\n呢位歷史上最仁愛寬厚既皇帝<br />\n打造左人類歷史上最繁華既朝代既極盛期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n北宋經濟點強唔洗我多講<br />\n政治上 北宋150年 三權制衡 不殺言官<br />\n加上社會思想開放<br />\n成就左亞洲首個最近似民主既國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n什麼文景之治 開皇之治 貞觀之治<br />\n相比起宋朝簡直係個塑膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n漢朝盛世左40年 唐朝盛世百餘年<br />\n但宋朝300都基本上處於盛世<br />\n<br />\n北宋可能比而家既中國更民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfe1330bbe3a5befd3f0777f2154c890d205db4","tid":2412493,"uid":384679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:22:51.000Z","msg":"聽講岳飛係比民意鋤死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班友仔唔想交多啲稅去收復同重建失土"},{"pid":"be9d915f37b491114982842c196f31ea51523be0","tid":2412493,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5305046092417ce885244681a02168855976b20","tid":2412493,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:32:31.000Z","msg":"邊三權？  軍權 皇權？"},{"pid":"6ea51918df159ebe33d9251281da0d7f3cb2069b","tid":2412493,"uid":147721,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:33:07.000Z","msg":"宋國還宋國 支国還支国 唔好混淆"},{"pid":"2d6f7dd0d732d8424b5fdb80a4e5cb1ebcc426e3","tid":2412493,"uid":320737,"like":1,"