like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:33:07.000Z","msg":"宋國還宋國 支国還支国 唔好混淆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:36:13.000Z","msg":"宋朝後中國就亡左國了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:58:12.000Z","msg":"冇宋朝只有宋國<br />\n<br />\n當時有遼朝，金朝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:03:42.000Z","msg":"宋史中，宋人用&quot;中國&quot;指稱自己既，有三百幾例<br />\n用宋國自稱的，得1例<br />\n係講向元投降，入表曰&quot;「宋國主臣 謹百拜奉表言...」<br />\n<br />\n另一例係列轉第二十既「論曰」，係元人論宋，<br />\n「論曰：太祖事漢、周，同時將校多聯事兵間，及分藩立朝，位或相亞。宋國建，皆折其猛悍不可屈之氣，俛首改事，且為盡力焉。」"},{"pid":"2b01733f8fc552977898a9f05219ddd251a82819","tid":2412493,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:04:12.000Z","msg":"你自己都話是「宋朝」，係「宋國」，又點會係「中國」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，打你老母臭閪造<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a690ae5623ec00a6c3d8218644da7b706905c60d","tid":2412493,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"550fe5a6148471a7dd232a85c7abbe63fc424551","tid":2412493,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ea51918df159ebe33d9251281da0d7f3cb2069b","tid":2412493,"uid":147721,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:33:07.000Z","msg":"宋國還宋國 支国還支国 唔好混淆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"單係 宋史 君臣自稱中國既，大概三百幾條<br />\n由古至清，其實每個自命正統既皇朝都自命中國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:06:08.000Z","msg":"係 所以搞清楚一點 宋國還宋國 支国還支国 呢啲真係國黎<br />\n而「中國」係一個玩爛左既term 並唔係指一個實際存在既國家 甚至唔係指一個抽象意義上既國家<br />\n要類比既話 「中國」呢個term同政權 兩者之間既關係<br />\n就好似「皇帝」呢個頭銜同拎住呢個頭銜既人既關係咁<br />\n<br />\n或者簡單啲講 宋國宰相同支国縂理 係毫無關係 雖然佢地都自稱係中國最高職位既官員"},{"pid":"01fa6129833d55f4709ac534ae1ec46c629a1449","tid":2412493,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T06:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653b1925252fdf8b4a311767112814110e0828d0","tid":2412493,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efe1c0be244752160aa52f019071f63b8c255e4","tid":2412493,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c08825dff8cfd3473250f2cb3626f29a6e7235","tid":2412493,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T09:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f45f79e65a5d9dc82b22297fdf0a71f9003b21d","tid":2412493,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:29:29.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}